<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-0936 </DOCNO><TEXT>The disclosure relates to low loss, high power variable attenuators comprisingone or more transmissive and/or reflective multilayer dielectric filters.The attenuator is particularly suitable to use with unpolarized laserssuch as excimer lasers. Beam attenuation is a function of beam polarizationand the angle of incidence between the beam and the filter and is controlledby adjusting the angle of incidence the beam makes to the filter or filters.Filters are selected in accordance with beam wavelength. 9 figs.</TEXT></DOC>